A cyberpunk-style digital visualization of two parallel data streams racing through a neon-lit circuit board landscape. On one side, a sleek narrow river of glowing cyan particles flows efficiently through a streamlined channel, representing focused database queries. On the other side, a massive sprawling network of magenta energy tendrils spreads outward, touching and illuminating thousands of tiny floating document icons before converging back. The scene is set against a dark backdrop of towering server monoliths with holographic grids. Rain falls through volumetric light beams, creating atmospheric depth. The contrast between the efficient narrow stream and the expansive branching search pattern is stark and dramatic, with electric sparks where data points connect.
